longBusinessSummary: Matmown, Inc., along with its subsidiaries, explores, produces, and acquires gold properties in Peru and Chile. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada with additional offices in Lima, Peru; and Santiago, Chile.
